n support of the efforts of the Union for International Cancer Control|url=http://www.uicc.org/raymond-weil-0|journal=The Union for International Cancer Control|access-date=2014-02-05|archive-date=2012-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510065554/http://www.uicc.org/raymond-weil-0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=A Limited Edition to Support Fight Against Cancer|url=http://www.worldtempus.com/en/news/top-news/detail/article/1282725711-raymond-weil-a-limited-edition-to-support-fight-against-cancer/|journal=Worldtempus|date=25 August 2010|access-date=2014-02-05|archive-date=2010-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100829142852/http://www.worldtempus.com/en/news/top-news/detail/article/1282725711-raymond-weil-a-limited-edition-to-support-fight-against-cancer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

