'''VH1拯救音乐基金会（VH1 Save The Music Foundation）：'''蕾蒙威对其款系的命名显然表明，音乐是该品牌的核心，而且音乐也是其身份的体现，蕾蒙威于2011年开始与VH1拯救音乐基金会合作，该基金会是一家慈善机构，致力于恢复美国音乐教育计划。这一合作在2011年通过蕾蒙威官方Facebook页面上的一项应用程序启动。粉丝可通过点击按钮向计数器添加1美元。计数器随着每次点击而不断更新，以显示蕾蒙威向该慈善机构的捐款数额。此外，该瑞士制表商还与VH1拯救音乐基金会组织的Elle女性音乐（Elle Women in Music）进行合作，于2012年4月在好莱坞举办的这一音乐盛典上拍卖由名人签名的腕表，这些名人包括杰西·J（Jessie J）、艾丽ˑ古尔丁（Ellie Goulding）、妮可ˑ斯彻金格（Nicole Scherzinger）和奥ˑ兰德（Oh Land）。此次拍卖销售所得款项全部捐赠给VH1拯救音乐基金会。<ref>{{cite web|title=VH1 Save The Music Foundation|url=http://www.vh1savethemusic.com/events/12|publisher=Official VH1 website|accessdate=2014-02-05|archive-date=2012-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116133844/http://vh1savethemusic.com/events/12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=ELLE announces third annual woman in music 2012|url=http://www.vh1savethemusic.com/node/5837|publisher=VH1 Save The Music Foundation|date =27 March 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Charity Bids Launches RAYMOND WEIL Facebook Watch Auction to Benefit VH1 Save The Music Foundation|url=http://news.yahoo.com/charity-bids-launches-raymond-weil-facebook-watch-auction-184619026.html|publisher=Yahoo News|date =25 April 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Watch Auctioned to Benefit VH1 Save The Music Foundation|url=http://www.worldtempus.com/en/news/top-news/detail/article/1335432866-raymond-weil-encheres-online-pour-soutenir-la-vh1-save-the-music-foundation/|journal=Worldtempus|date=26 April 2012|access-date=2014-02-05|archive-date=2012-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120428110649/http://www.worldtempus.com/en/news/top-news/detail/article/1335432866-raymond-weil-encheres-online-pour-soutenir-la-vh1-save-the-music-foundation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=VH1 Save The Music's Songwriters Music Series Chicago Presented By RAYMOND WEIL And William Hill Estate Wines|url=http://www.zimbio.com/pictures/uMI5UY_U39D/VH1+Save+Music+Songwriters+Music+Series+Chicago|journal=Tasos Katopodis|date=26 April 2012|access-date=2014-02-05|archive-date=2013-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929231441/http://www.zimbio.com/pictures/uMI5UY_U39D/VH1+Save+Music+Songwriters+Music+Series+Chicago|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Robin Thicke at the VH1 Save The Music Foundation event wearing Raymond Weil|url=http://news.watchprosite.com/?show=forumpost&ti=787763&fi=112&s=0|publisher=watchprosite.com|date=26 April 2012|accessdate=2014-02-05|archive-date=2014-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225080312/http://news.watchprosite.com/?show=forumpost&ti=787763&fi=112&s=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''诺尔多夫-罗宾斯音乐治疗（Nordoff-Robbins Music Therapy）：''' 诺尔多夫-罗宾斯是英国最大的以音乐为导向的慈善机构之一。自2000年以来，蕾蒙威一直是该慈善机构的合作伙伴，与著名艺术家一起设计专属腕表，如拉玛（Lemar）和Jamiroquai乐队主唱杰伊ˑ凯（Jay Kay）。这些腕表在年度银色音符午宴（Silver Clef Lunch）上进行拍卖，拍卖所得款项全部捐赠给诺尔多夫-罗宾斯。2013年，公司授予美国吸血鬼周末（Vampire Weekend）乐队蕾蒙威国际艺术家奖（RAYMOND WEIL International Artist Award）。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Raymond Weil et Lemar, ensemble pour Nordoff-Robbins Music Therapy (in French)|url=http://www.worldtempus.com/fr/actualites/a-la-une/details/article/0-raymond-weil-et-lemar-ensemble-pour-nordoff-robbins-music-therapy/|journal=Worldtempus|date = 12 July 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Michael Bublé win the Raymond Weil International Award|url=http://www.nordoff-robbins.org.uk/news/michael-bubl%C3%A9-win-raymond-weil-international-award|journal=Nordoff Robbins|date=31 May 2012|access-date=2014-02-05|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223205334/http://www.nordoff-robbins.org.uk/news/michael-bubl%C3%A9-win-raymond-weil-international-award|dead-url=no}}</ref> En 2013, la compañía presentó el American band Vampire Weekend con el premio al artista internacional RAYMOND WEIL. <ref>{{cite journal|title=Award Winners 2013|url=http://www.nordoff-robbins.org.uk/content/get-involved/support-event/nordoff-robbins-o2-silver-clef-awards/2013-award-winners|journal=Nordoff Robbins|access-date=2014-02-05|archive-date=2013-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728185142/http://www.nordoff-robbins.org.uk/content/get-involved/support-event/nordoff-robbins-o2-silver-clef-awards/2013-award-winners|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''世界野生动物基金会（WWF）：'''蕾蒙威是在瑞士蒙特勒举办的2007 WWF熊猫舞会（Panda Ball Gala）的官方合作伙伴。该舞会上组织了彩票活动，为保护地中海募集资金，蕾蒙威提供了彩票活动的一等奖：一枚镶嵌钻石的18K金Parsifal腕表。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Premier Prix du Gala Panda Ball du WWF (in French)|url=http://www.worldtempus.com/fr/actualites/a-la-une/details/article/0-raymond-weil-geneve-premier-prix-du-gala-panda-ball-du-wwf/|journal=Worldtempus|date = 14 May 2007}}</ref> 

